</div><p><i>Sarah Zhang is a science journalist based in Washington, DC. Follow her on Twitter <a href="http://www.twitter.com/sarahzhang" target="_blank">@sarahzhang</a>.</i><br></p><p><i>This classic Facts So Romantic post was originally published in September, 2013.</i></p><p><i><br></i></p>

